Package commands

Interface Summary
Command Interface for Undo/Redo operations.
CommandFilter  
 

Class Summary
AddElementCommand Class provides Undo/Redo operations for adding new Element.
AddElementCommandFilter Filters element adding command if it is wrong.
AddElementInvoker Provides executing of Undo/Redo operations for adding of Element.
ChangePlaceValuesCommand Class provides Undo/Redo operations for changing of Place.
ChangePlaceValuesInvoker Provides executing of Undo/Redo operations for changing of Place.
ChangeTransitionValuesCommand Class provides Undo/Redo operations for changing of Transition.
ChangeTransitionValuesInvoker Provides executing of Undo/Redo operations for changing of Transition.
CommandStack Stack of the commands, It is used for Undo/Redo operations, It provides saving of commands and executing the commands.
DeleteElementCommand Class provides Undo/Redo operations for adding new Element.
DeleteElementInvoker Provides executing of Undo/Redo operations for deleting of Elements.
